## Proposed Changes

### Operator Core

#### [MODIFY] [agentic-chat-executor.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/agentic-chat-executor.ts)
- Replace the `break;` statement when `!result` is true with an early return that includes `"LLM returned no response."` or the actual accumulated content.

#### [MODIFY] [llm-provider-manager.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/llm-provider-manager.ts)
- Inspect the supervisor's slot status when `dynamicPort` is missing. If the slot status is `"error"`, throw a detailed `Error` bubbling the actual slot startup failure reason.

